Arlette Marchal https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arlette_Marchal 0 Arlette Marchal (29 January 1902 – 11 February 1984) was a French film actress. She appeared in 41 films between 1922 and 1951. She was born and died in Paris. Arlette_Marchal ( 29_January_1902 – 11_February_1984 ) was a_French_film_actress . She appeared in 41_films between 1922_and_1951 . She was_born and died in Paris .
